    "code": "a = [1, 2]\n\nimport flopscope as fnp\n\nfnp.asarray(a)\n\na = fnp.array([1, 2])\n\nfnp.asarray(a) is a\n\na = fnp.array([1, 2], dtype=fnp.float32)\n\nfnp.shares_memory(fnp.asarray(a, dtype=fnp.float32), a)\n\nfnp.shares_memory(fnp.asarray(a, dtype=fnp.float64), a)\n\nissubclass(fnp.recarray, fnp.ndarray)\n\na = fnp.array([(1., 2), (3., 4)], dtype='f4,i4').view(fnp.recarray)\n\nfnp.asarray(a) is a\n\nfnp.asanyarray(a) is a",
    "output": "array([1, 2])\n\nTrue\n\nTrue\n\nFalse\n\nTrue\n\nFalse\n\nTrue",
